    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You empower your body with your frost release chakra to move at much faster speeds. Move up to your movement speed to a point you can see within range, that you could move to. This movement counts as teleportation.</p><p>If this jutsu was used as a reaction, you instead move up to half of your movement speed. If this was used against an Attack, the attack gains disadvantage on the attack roll. If this was used against a Saving Throw, you gain advantage on the save.</p>",
